cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR

The paper deals with computer vision tasks related to 3D representation learning, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves object-centric camera pose estimation and feature matching, which are related to robotics (cs.RO). The paper uses a multi-task ConvNet to learn a generic 3D representation, which is a machine learning approach (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with foundational tasks related to 3D, which could be considered as a topic in computer graphics (cs.GR).
